title: Insane game PC (2001)
description:
Very good game from 2001.
Just unzip and play.

Minimal system requirements:
----------------------------
  CPU: Pentium II 233MHz CPU

  RAM: 64MB RAM

  GPU: DirectX 7.0 compatibile 3D graphics card with 8MB RAM

  HDD: 100 MB hard disk space

  Sound: 16-bit DirectX compatibile sound card

  Note: SUPPORTED 3D CHIPSETS: 3Dfx Voodoo 2, Voodoo Banshee, Voodoo3, Voodoo5 ATI Rage 128, Radeon Matrox G200, G400 Nvidia Riva TNT, Riva TNT2 GeForce 256, GeForce 2 S3 Savage 2000
